WEBVTT

00:01:25.720 --> 00:01:31.072
that I had wasted a seat
by marrying a non-medico.

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:33.248
He also added

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:40.040
"If you wanted to marry a Dhillon,
you could have chosen your class mate."

00:01:40.040 --> 00:01:41.791
(Laughter)

00:01:41.791 --> 00:01:45.940
(Cheers and applause)

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:51.018
I was very disappointed
that I could not practice,

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:55.695
but my parents used to urge me
to face disappointment bravely.

00:01:56.040 --> 00:01:57.584
And that was what I did.

00:01:57.920 --> 00:01:59.674
It was not easy,

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:02.696
but I kept doing part time voluntary work.